{"id":987662080,"question_id":3,"lang":"java","lang_name":"Java","time":"11 months, 1 week","timestamp":1688636362,"status":10,"status_display":"Accepted","runtime":"8 ms","url":"/submissions/detail/987662080/","is_pending":"Not Pending","title":"Longest Substring Without Repeating Characters","memory":"43.9 MB","code":"class Solution {\n    public int lengthOfLongestSubstring(String s) {\n        int max = 0;\n        \n        int len = s.length();\n        \n        HashSet<Character> set =new HashSet<>();\n        \n        \n        int left = 0;\n        for(int right=0; right<len; right++){\n            \n            char ch = s.charAt(right);\n            \n                \n            while(left<right && set.contains(ch)){\n                char chh = s.charAt(left);\n                set.remove(chh);\n                left++;\n            }\n            \n            max = Math.max(max, right-left+1);\n            set.add(ch);\n        }\n        \n        return max;\n    }\n}","compare_result":"","title_slug":"longest-substring-without-repeating-characters","has_notes":false,"flag_type":1}
